cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper's focus on developing a decoding algorithm suggests that it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the potential application of simultaneous translation in computer vision tasks suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision).
